<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">数同求积法，是指求由n个2与n个5组成的两个n位数的积。此法，可从1写到n，再从n-1写到1，后面添写一个0，此数即为所求的积。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">222×555=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=123210</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>